<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 负责保存流亡者记录并分析战前数据，确保没有任何有价值的东西随时间流失。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.title>档案管理员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.titleShort>档案管理员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 维持巡逻队和营地之间的无线电联系，协调任务并在荒地上传递重要信息。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.title>传讯官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.titleShort>通讯官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 为被放逐者的营地提供食物，用任何能捡到的东西准备食物，并通过每顿饭来鼓舞士气。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.title>被遗弃的厨师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.titleShort>厨师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 专门从事爆炸物、清除障碍和破坏敌方防御工事以进行流亡者行动。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.title>爆破专家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.titleShort>拆除</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 与荒地定居点和敌对派系进行谈判，结成联盟并为流放者的生存获取资源。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.title>被遗弃的外交官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.titleShort>外交官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 不断晋升，指挥流亡者小队，以战术精确度协调袭击和防御行动。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.title>战地指挥官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.titleShort>指挥官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 向流亡者新兵传授荒地生存的严酷现实，从觅食到野外维修和战斗训练。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.title>现场讲师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.titleShort>讲师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 前往荒地研究变异的动植物群，为流放者提供宝贵的科学见解和生存知识。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.title>实地研究员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.titleShort>研究员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在武器操作、战术和生存方面训练新的流亡者新兵，塑造下一代战士。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.title>讲师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.titleShort>讲师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 协调流亡者营地之间的物资和人员流动，确保每个小队都有生存和战斗所需的东西。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.title>物流主任</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.titleShort>后勤</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 维护流亡者的车辆和设备，确保每台机器都做好随时战斗的准备。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.title>被遗弃的机械师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.titleShort>机械</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 成为一名熟练的医生，治疗受伤的流放者并开发新的野战医学技术以在荒地生存。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.title>医务官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.titleShort>军医</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] became an expert in maintaining and piloting power armor, leading Outcast charges into the most 危险 battles.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.title>动力装甲专家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.titleShort>装甲专家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 管理流亡者的军械库和补给品，确保每个小队都有生存和战斗所需的装备。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.title>军需</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.titleShort>军需</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 擅长侦察敌人阵地和收集情报，经常为流放者冒险深入敌对领土。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.title>侦察专家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.titleShort>侦察</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.description>[PAWN_nameDef] led expeditions into 危险 废墟s, recovering valuable technology and resources to keep the Outcasts supplied and operational.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.title>被遗弃的打捞者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.titleShort>打捞者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.description>[PAWN_nameDef] led reconnaissance teams through the 废墟s, mapping safe routes and identifying threats before they could strike at the Outcasts.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.title>侦察队长</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.titleShort>侦察队长</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 致力于 [PAWN_possessive] 的一生来保存流放者的知识并对每一项恢复的技术和知识进行编目。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.title>被遗弃的抄写员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.titleShort>隶</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 早年花费 [PAWN_possessive] 帮助流亡者档案管理员保存和研究战前文件，了解历史和记录保存的重要性。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.title>档案员助理</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.titleShort>档案管理员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在流放者的地下掩体中出生和长大，从小就学习纪律、谨慎和每一种资源的价值。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.title>地堡诞生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.titleShort>地堡诞生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 被分配到流亡者的医疗舱，学习了基本的急救和分诊，为前线的现实生活做好准备。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.title>战地军医乡绅</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.titleShort>战地医疗兵</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在车间度过了 [PAWN_possessive] 童年，学习修理和维护流放者的技术和车辆，确保他们的运作顺利进行。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.title>被遗弃的机械师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.titleShort>机械</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 通过协助被遗弃的医务人员学习了医学基础知识，培养了急救和伤员护理技能。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.title>被遗弃的医生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.titleShort>军医</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 通过在流放者的食堂帮助组织膳食和补给品，确保每个人都有饭吃，学会了责任感和团队合作。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.title>食堂管家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.titleShort>混乱管家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.description>着迷于动力装甲，[PAWN_nameDef]花费了无数时间学习维护并最终操作这些流放者力量的象征。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.title>动力装甲实习生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.titleShort>铠甲实习生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 接受过侦察兵训练，学习在荒地中航行并收集敌人动向的情报，确保兄弟会流亡者的安全。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.title>被遗弃的侦察兵</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.titleShort>侦察</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在年轻的侦察兵中扮演了领导角色，引导他们穿过荒地并教他们生存所需的技能。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.title>被遗弃的童子军领袖</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.titleShort>童军领袖</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.description>[PAWN_nameDef] was chosen by an Outcast Scribe for early mentorship, learning to read, write, and analyze 古老 texts and schematics.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.title>文士的学生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.titleShort>文士的学生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 负责在流放者营地之间运送物资，了解在严酷的荒地中速度和可靠性的重要性。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.title>被遗弃的补给跑者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.titleShort>供应跑者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 很早就表现出了技术天赋，协助 Outcast 工程师抢救和恢复战前设备。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.title>技术学徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.titleShort>技术学徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.description>由于荒原的危险而成为孤儿，[PAWN_nameDef] 被流放者收养，并很快适应了他们严酷的生存主义生活方式。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.title>废土孤儿</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.titleShort>孤儿</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.description>小时候，[PAWN_nameDef] 经常出现在流放者的工作室中，在资深机械师的指导下学习修理武器和盔甲。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.title>车间帮手</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.titleShort>车间帮手</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 一直对人类历史感兴趣，这让 [PAWN_possessive] 被遗弃的老师很恼火，他们更喜欢教授更多“实用”的东西。 [PAWN_pronoun] 经常通过非传统方式获取知识。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.title>年轻历史学家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.titleShort>历史学家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 成为了以土地为生的专家，教导其他人如何狩猎、觅食以及忍受荒地可能提供的最恶劣的条件。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.title>生存主义者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.titleShort>生存主义者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.description>[PAWN_nameDef] earned a reputation as a stalwart protector of Outcast camps, h老旧ing the line against raiders and mutants with unwavering resolve.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.title>老将后卫</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.titleShort>后卫</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.titleShort>
</LanguageData>
